# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:10
translate french micha13_66a911ed:

    # "When I get to the counselor's office, I'm surprised to see Gertrude behind the counter instead of Mi-Cha."
    "Quand j'arrive au bureau de la conseillère, je suis surpris de voir Gertrude derrière le comptoir à la place de Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:11
translate french micha13_51f359cb:

    # sc "Good morning, [pcname]. If you're here for a counseling session, I'm sorry. I have to work reception today."
    sc "Bonjour, [pcname]. Si tu es là pour une séance de conseil, je suis désolée. Je dois m'occuper de l'accueil aujourd'hui."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:12
translate french micha13_320f7ecc:

    # pc "Where's Mi-Cha?"
    pc "Où est Mi-Cha ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:13
translate french micha13_f822911c:

    # sc "She called this morning saying she couldn't come in for some reason. She sounded upset."
    sc "Elle a appelé ce matin pour dire qu’elle ne pouvait pas venir pour une raison quelconque. Elle avait l’air bouleversée."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:14
translate french micha13_d6ed663d:

    # sc "If you have time, maybe you could go check on her? I know you two have become friends."
    sc "Si tu as le temps, tu pourrais peut-être aller voir comment elle va ? Je sais que vous êtes devenus amis."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:15
translate french micha13_477e82cd:

    # pc "Yeah, I think I have a little time before class. I'll go do that."
    pc "Oui, je crois que j’ai un peu de temps avant le cours. Je vais y aller."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:18
translate french micha13_cfda0a84:

    # "I leave the counselor's office, walk over to the dorms, and make my way up to Mi-Cha's door."
    "Je quitte le bureau de la conseillère, je me dirige vers les dortoirs et je monte jusqu’à la porte de Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:22
translate french micha13_90464c94:

    # "She answers after a couple of knocks."
    "Elle répond après quelques coups."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:23
translate french micha13_94a711d9:

    # mc "Oh, [pcname]! Why are you here?"
    mc "Oh, [pcname] ! Pourquoi es-tu là ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:24
translate french micha13_36eedc65:

    # pc "Gertrude asked me to come check on you. She said you called in. Are you sick?"
    pc "Gertrude m’a demandé de venir voir si tout allait bien. Elle m’a dit que tu avais appelé. Tu es malade ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:25
translate french micha13_2e46b23a:

    # mc "No, I'm not sick."
    mc "Non, je ne suis pas malade."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:26
translate french micha13_cb45e08c:

    # pc "Well, what's going on?"
    pc "Eh bien, qu’est-ce qui se passe ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:29
translate french micha13_98c909b0:

    # "I follow her inside and we sit on her bed."
    "Je la suis à l’intérieur et nous nous asseyons sur son lit."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:30
translate french micha13_2f43efba:

    # mc "I argued with my parents last night. They told me to quit dance class. They say that it interferes with my studies."
    mc "Je me suis disputée avec mes parents hier soir. Ils m’ont dit d’arrêter les cours de danse. Ils disent que ça nuit à mes études."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:31
translate french micha13_6282a1b7:

    # pc "But you like dancing."
    pc "Mais tu aimes danser."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:34
translate french micha13_44899e27:

    # mc "I love dancing. And I have a performance soon that I was very much looking forward to."
    mc "J'adore danser. Et j'ai bientôt un spectacle que j'attendais avec impatience."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:35
translate french micha13_4624f9be:

    # mc "But they say that I have to stop."
    mc "Mais ils disent que je dois arrêter."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:36
translate french micha13_ff3c6bab:

    # pc "So what?"
    pc "Et alors ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:37
translate french micha13_f0ac6ad2:

    # mc "I can't just not do what they say."
    mc "Je ne peux pas simplement ne pas faire ce qu'ils disent."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:40
translate french micha13_23d549c1:

    # pc "But I want you to dance."
    pc "Mais je veux que tu danses."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:41
translate french micha13_81709362:

    # mc "You do?"
    mc "Vraiment ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:42
translate french micha13_6dba6230:

    # pc "Yes."
    pc "Oui."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:43
translate french micha13_27a4c741:

    # mc "Are you telling me to?"
    mc "Tu me dis de le faire ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:44
translate french micha13_f43da382:

    # pc "Yes, Mi-Cha. I'm telling you to dance."
    pc "Oui, Mi-Cha. Je te dis de danser."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:49
translate french micha13_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yessir.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yessir.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:50
translate french micha13_620baac7:

    # mc "Yes, [mcsir]."
    mc "Oui, [mcsir]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:51
translate french micha13_929f424d:

    # pc "So you will?"
    pc "Alors tu vas le faire ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:54
translate french micha13_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yessir.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yessir.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:55
translate french micha13_620baac7_1:

    # mc "Yes, [mcsir]."
    mc "Oui, [mcsir]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:56
translate french micha13_536da0ad:

    # mc "I will keep dancing. For you."
    mc "Je vais continuer à danser. Pour toi."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:57
translate french micha13_f07574ec:

    # pc "Good."
    pc "Bien."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:61
translate french micha13_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:62
translate french micha13_5b61e929:

    # mc "Thank you, [pcname]."
    mc "Merci, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:63
translate french micha13_e3b6df4e:

    # pc "Do you feel better now?"
    pc "Tu te sens mieux maintenant ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:64
translate french micha13_c324b928:

    # mc "Yes. I feel much better now."
    mc "Oui. Je me sens beaucoup mieux maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:65
translate french micha13_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "D'accord."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:66
translate french micha13_c98760d6:

    # mc "I'll get dressed and go to the office."
    mc "Je vais m'habiller et aller au bureau."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:70
translate french micha13_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/micha_imsorry2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_imsorry2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:71
translate french micha13_5fbcf7dd:

    # mc "I'm sorry you had to see me like this. In my pajamas with no makeup."
    mc "Je suis désolée que tu aies dû me voir comme ça. En pyjama et sans maquillage."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:72
translate french micha13_57c13e1f:

    # pc "Don't be silly. You're gorgeous."
    pc "Ne sois pas bête. Tu es magnifique."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:75
translate french micha13_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/micha_thankyousir2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_thankyousir2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:76
translate french micha13_b00529b9:

    # mc "Thank you, [mcsir]."
    mc "Merci, [mcsir]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:79
translate french micha13_80adb898:

    # "I kiss her goodbye."
    "Je l'embrasse pour lui dire au revoir."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:80
translate french micha13_bed52260:

    # "If I had time, I'd do more."
    "Si j'avais le temps, j'irais plus loin."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:83
translate french micha13_1a383b4b:

    # "But I have to get to class, so we pull apart and I tell her goodbye."
    "Mais je dois aller en cours, alors on s'écarte l'un de l'autre et je lui dis au revoir."

